  # Transcript API
  
  Endpoints for managing continuous transcript text storage, segmented by day/hour, with semantic AI querying capabilities.
  
  ## Features
  - Ingest transcript chunks (10-20 seconds of text)
  - Automatic daily chatroom creation per user
  - Hour-based segment organization
  - NLP analysis (sentiment + topics)
  - Vector embeddings for semantic search
  - Daily and weekly summaries
}
